    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "oh okay that makes sense. so if the maillard reaction needs amino acids too, does that mean i could potentially speed it up or make it more intense by adding certain things to the dough? like if i added more protein or sugar, would that change the browning? i'm just trying to get a better handle on the chemistry of why some crusts get way darker than others.",
